</listitem>
                    <listitem><para>Once L3 and metadata neutron agents are stopped, follow steps 1 through 7 in
                        the document <xref linkend="without_dvr"/> and
                        then run the <literal>neutron-reconfigure.yml</literal> playbook:
                        </para>
<screen >cd ~/scratch/ansible/next/hos/ansible
ansible-playbook -i hosts/verb_hosts neutron-reconfigure.yml</screen></listitem>
                </orderedlist>
